name: The Love is Here- Limited edition prints
description:
Limited edition prints (1-10).

There are a total of 35 artworks which, formed the Love is Here exhibition at Rancho Notorious in Melbourne and aMBUSH Gallery in Sydney. 

To see all of the 35 artworks available please visit the 'photos' section of our Facebook page here:

http://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Love-is-Here-Book-Launch-and-Exhibition/191128420925370?sk=photos

Limited edition prints are printed at A3 on a 210GSM, satin gloss stock in black and white, and printed locally in Australia.

name: The Love is Here Book
description:
A beautifully finished 25 page, A5 book is a compilation of 25 individual artworks in response to a national callout (Australia) to create a visual response in black and white to a set of words. And those words…'I love you'.

Idea being that there are many ways to say ‘I love you’, to see some of the diverse range of responses submitted please visit our Facebook page at:

http://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Love-is-Here-Book-Launch-and-Exhibition/191128420925370

The book is black and white, printed on recycled paper by local Australian companies, wrapped in a 'Moleskin' type recycled card cover and perfect bound so that the individual artworks/pages can be torn out and given to people as little loving gifts in a 'pay it forward kind of way'.

Book was launched at Rancho Notorious Gallery in Melbourne in July 2011, and aMBUSH Gallery in Sydney in August 2011, and now available in selected bookstores and online.
